{"tid":2499631,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"高達UC世紀，二號機的咀咒","createTime":"2021-04-22T04:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T07:24:02.000Z","uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a9130d8b82b22ecaac9baa2450f36950caac7efa","tid":2499631,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T04:53:46.000Z","msg":"2號機的咀咒<br />\n<br />\n在UC世紀，有一個有關高達2號機的咀咒---但凡由聯邦開發既2號機，往往都會被偷走<br />\n<br />\n開啟咀咒既係元祖高達RX-78-2<br />\n本來有RX-78三架機準備測試，自護軍發現，最終RX-78-2被平民少年阿寶意外開動，雖然阿寶加入軍隊，但登上機體時，佢本身未被授權，都算係偷。<br />\n<br />\n正式被敵方偷走既高達2號機  RX-79BD-2<br />\n搭載EXAM系統既BD系列，基礎係陸戰型高達，1號機係GM頭。<br />\n2號機改為高達頭，被自護軍搶走。<br />\n<br />\n最出名既被盜2號機  RX-78GP02<br />\nAE開發，以運用核武為目標既機體，被自護殘黨達拉斯艦隊搶走，成功在所羅門以核彈大破聯邦檢閱艦隊<br />\n<br />\n成個系列被搶走既2號機  RX-178 MKII<br />\n聯邦特殊部門泰坦斯開發，共3部，測試時過被奧干搶走2架，最後一架被原泰垣斯既愛瑪中尉駕走，投誠奧干。<br />\n<br />\n被轉換陣營的巨人 PSYCHO GUNDAM MK-II<br />\n原由泰坦斯開發及使用，被奧干Z高達擊破，之彼被阿古哲斯新自護接手，改良後再與奧干對戰<br />\n<br />\nF90-2<br />\n外傳故事，聯邦以新一代高達雙機實驗機F-90鎮壓火星獨立軍，F-90 2號機獨立軍於部隊內應搶走，最終與1號機對決大破"},{"pid":"ec0e94e2ccfd7e72e5b1142e7d9927ccec8fddaa","tid":2499631,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T05:52:35.000Z","msg":"波蕾二世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8575f5fe8c8c021151cdc9e34abf283edf92ef","tid":2499631,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"海盜高達X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b346c87b414953ca3744e6156029a7ecd962bd","tid":2499631,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb8575f5fe8c8c021151cdc9e34abf283edf92ef","tid":2499631,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"海盜高達X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"屌，漏左<br />\n<br />\n因咩只有2號機成日被偷？"},{"pid":"a0dab727b9d29a8469bfa95efe1c6de194dc17f7","tid":2499631,"uid":186882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e2b346c87b414953ca3744e6156029a7ecd962bd","tid":2499631,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb8575f5fe8c8c021151cdc9e34abf283edf92ef","tid":2499631,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"海盜高達X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"屌，漏左<br />\n<br />\n因咩只有2號機成日被偷？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"因為試作型慣咗整兩部啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有RX-0 2號機<br />\n<br />\n非UC既有呢部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXaJBY5wCFeupdcdqZ9TFQopgFUqkqD7VWxAJ5wPbtzgK?filename=sPicib9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsPicib9.png&h=0e8f7547&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22f58fb2723b9ffeefe8140e8814c38e96e4aed2","tid":2499631,"uid":187412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b346c87b414953ca3744e6156029a7ecd962bd","tid":2499631,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb8575f5fe8c8c021151cdc9e34abf283edf92ef","tid":2499631,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"海盜高達X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"屌，漏左<br />\n<br />\n因咩只有2號機成日被偷？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:29:29.000Z","msg":"獨角獸算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb3888b3218da0e73f11e773f9e93f08fa608b1","tid":2499631,"uid":287107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22f58fb2723b9ffeefe8140e8814c38e96e4aed2","tid":2499631,"uid":187412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b346c87b414953ca3744e6156029a7ecd962bd","tid":2499631,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"