都係財團自己生產，係3號機先係EFSF自己整結果有瑕疵先搞到有爆走事件同0097<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75e7b3d859457e96332e2564a62def6f0a8325e","tid":2499631,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eee040f8842b6ca8209f5d66c6ed3c8f2645fdf5","tid":2499631,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"其實獨角獸二號機算唔算屬於EFSF<br />\n<br />\n本身1，2號機都係財團自己生產，係3號機先係EFSF自己整結果有瑕疵先搞到有爆走事件同0097<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"一直以為2號機係偷1號機資料整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇翻設定原來一開始已經係整兩部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係財團一直都keep一號機咁啱肥馬想偷機被個孫揸走咗"},{"pid":"7c3f210464ed361ddef9cea701cfb7cd0cfa7eb0","tid":2499631,"uid":326140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"W G unit 02<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}